    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a masterpiece of automotive history, a vehicle that doesn't just drive, but breathes with the soul of a bygone era. This pristine specimen glows with a luster that captures the golden hour even at midnight, its curves whispering stories of moonlit coastal runs and high-stakes elegance. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of untouched heritage, where the scent of rich, preserved materials transports you to a world of absolute refinement. To own this car is to possess a living legend, a flawless time capsule that demands attention not through volume, but through an undeniable, quiet authority. It isn't just a car; it's the protagonist of your next great adventure.",
      "price": 48500.0,
